question: Radha Yadav, who took part in the ICC T20 World Cup 2020 Women's team of India belongs from which of the following district of Uttar Pradesh?
explanation: Radha Yadav, who took part in the T20 World Cup Women's team of India belongs to Jaunpur district (Ajoshi village) of Uttar Pradesh. The women's team of Australia won the ICC T20 World Cup 2020.
